{"tid":569213,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"肥絲晚上離世 車保羅悲慟：見唔到佢最後一面","createTime":"2018-02-22T13:20:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-22T13:40:04.000Z","uid":128737,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4734dcd2b12804613585af01bd687e8066598c07","tid":569213,"uid":128737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T13:20:51.000Z","msg":"【《審死官》拍檔】肥施施介強晚上離世 車保羅悲慟：見唔到佢最後一面<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180222/large/1519304274_f48b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180222%2Flarge%2F1519304274_f48b.jpg&h=84a37805&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一個身高6呎3，一個體重曾經超過300磅，58歲的車保羅，與比他年長兩歲的施介強（肥施）是一對活孖寶，90年代接戲接到手軟，除咗歷蘇主演嘅《香港也瘋狂》同《危情》等等之外，最令人深刻的當然是《審死官》中的瘦虎肥龍。去年初兩人一齊接受《蘋果》專訪笑談近況，今日突傳來肥施離世的消息。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180222/57863346\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180222%2F57863346&d=6Ibac1x%2BSHndQM8TaMg4W54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=750c0b1d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180222%2F57863346&h=c683ed2f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180222/57863346</a>"},{"pid":"e05e29d8a7906db65b511a7f209fc5e75a4f70f6","tid":569213,"uid":42188,"like":17,"dislike":3,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T13:23:08.000Z","msg":"肥絲死左，死埋右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6900eb650a42dcb44d92ffa5b6347b1e1788c7be","tid":569213,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"e05e29d8a7906db65b511a7f209fc5e75a4f70f6","tid":569213,"uid":42188,"like":17,"dislike":3,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T13:23:08.000Z","msg":"肥絲死左，死埋右<img src=\"/assets/f